controller.appointment
The classes in this package provide the necessary components and functionalities to handle the needs of the Doctor, Patient and Pharmacists in scheduling appointments, recording of the appointment outcomes and viewing it.

The class in this package provide the necessary components and functionalities for Users to manage the security of their account and login to the application.

The classes in this package provide the necessary components and functionalities to handle the needs of Doctor, Patient, and Pharmacists.

The class in this package provide the necessary components and functionalities for Pharmacists and Administrators to handle replenishment requests.
controller.user
The classes in this package handles the methods that achieves the functionalities required of each user in the application.
